Read the filename, NAME and ACC identifiers from a profile HMM into a list.

Source: R/io-methods.R
multi_read_padloc_model.Rd

Read the filename, NAME and ACC identifiers from a profile HMM into a list.

Usage

multi_read_padloc_model(directory)

Arguments

directory

Path to a directory containing profile HMMs (*.hmm)

Value

A base::list().

Examples

multi_read_hmm_header(padlocdev_example("hmm"))
#> $PROT00001
#> $PROT00001$`HMMER3/f`
#> [1] "[3.3 | Nov 2019]"
